author: cmpilato
msg: Fix a bug that caused a loop which searches successive parent
directories for the WebDAV VCC to quit after a single iteration.
(This code wasn't exercised lately by the trunk test suite because it
only runs when HTTPv2 isn't available.)
(svn_ra_serf__discover_vcc): Fix while() condition to avoid bailing
out of loop too early.  While here, correct an error message that
referred to an OPTIONS request when a PROPFIND was used.
